### Get all comments
GET http://localhost:5001/api/comments

### Create a new comment
POST http://localhost:5001/api/comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "file_id": "<uuid>",
  "user_id": "<uuid>",
  "comment": "Great lecture!",
  "parent_id": null,
  "likes": 0
}

### Get a comment by ID
GET http://localhost:5001/api/comments/<uuid>
